{"type":"message","id":"ee0186d3","parentId":"505d3b32","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:23:23.975Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"太好了！我已经获取到了数据结构。现在我需要创建一个Python脚本来批量抓取所有历史数据。从数据中我可以看到：\n\n- 期号：26048（表示2026年第48期）\n- 前区号码（红球）：5个数字\n- 后区（蓝球）：2个数字\n- 其他信息：奖池奖金、一等奖、二等奖、总投注额、开奖日期\n\n现在我需要：\n1. 创建数据库初始化脚本\n2. 创建数据抓取脚本\n3. 创建查询脚本\n\n让我先关闭浏览器，然后创建脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_627e018454324293b6cefabd","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"agent-browser close"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":9374,"output":257,"cacheRead":74432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84063,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778073791733,"responseId":"20260506212312e9af3e62067445ec"}}
{"type":"message","id":"654f13b9","parentId":"ee0186d3","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:23:24.211Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_627e018454324293b6cefabd","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[32m✓[0m Browser closed"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":230,"aggregated":"[32m✓[0m Browser closed","cwd":"/workspace/projects/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1778073804211}}
{"type":"message","id":"e4ca70cf","parentId":"654f13b9","timestamp":"2026-05-06T13:23:40.286Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，浏览器已关闭。现在让我创建大乐透技能的脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"现在让我创建大乐透技能的脚本。先创建数据库初始化脚本："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_88d8edb435c14f89bbcfc8c5","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n大乐透数据库初始化脚本\n创建SQLite数据库和表结构\n\"\"\"\n\nimport sqlite3\nimport os\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\n# 数据库文件路径\nDB_PATH = Path(__file__).parent.parent / \"data\" / \"super_lotto.db\"\n\ndef init_database():\n    \"\"\"初始化数据库\"\"\"\n    # 确保数据目录存在\n    DB_PATH.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n    \n    conn = sqlite3.connect(DB_PATH)\n    cursor = conn.cursor()\n    \n    # 创建开奖记录表\n    # 大乐透规则：\n    # - 前区（红球）：从01-35中选择5个号码\n    # - 后区（蓝球）：从01-12中选择2个号码\n    cursor.execute('''\n        CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS lottery_records (\n            id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,\n            issue_number TEXT UNIQUE NOT NULL,      -- 期号（如26048表示2026年第48期）\n            draw_date DATE NOT NULL,                -- 开奖日期\n            front_ball_1 INTEGER NOT NULL,          -- 前区（红球）1\n            front_ball_2 INTEGER NOT NULL,          -- 前区（红球）2\n            front_ball_3 INTEGER NOT NULL,          -- 前区（红球）3\n            front_ball_4 INTEGER NOT NULL,          -- 前区（红球）4\n            front_ball_5 INTEGER NOT NULL,          -- 前区（红球）5\n            back_ball_1 INTEGER NOT NULL,           -- 后区（蓝球）1\n            back_ball_2 INTEGER NOT NULL,           -- 后区（蓝球）2\n            pool_amount INTEGER,                    -- 奖池金额（分）\n            sales_amount INTEGER,                   -- 销售金额（分）\n            created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,\n            updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP\n        )\n    ''')\n    \n    # 创建索引\n    cursor.execute('CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_issue_number ON lottery_records(issue_number)')\n    cursor.execute('CREATE INDEX IF NOT EXISTS idx_draw_date ON lottery_records(draw_date)')\n    \n    conn.commit()\n    conn.close()\n    \n    print(f\"✅ 数据库初始化成功: {DB_PATH}\")\n    return DB_PATH\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    init_database()\n","path":"/workspace/projects/workspace/skills/super-lotto/scripts/init_db.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"coze","model":"auto","usage":{"input":180,"output":578,"cacheRead":83776,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84534,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1778073804213,"responseId":"20260506212324dff2d94f98864ede"}}
